mony and a broad social base through legal and extra-parliamentary struggles. An in-depth study of socio-economic circumstances that remain critical in conceptualizing radical extremism, Left Radicalism in India will be of interest to those studying Indian Politics, South Asian History, Development Studies and Global Politics"--cProvided by publisher.  a16 0aCommunismzIndiaxHistory. 0aCommunist partieszIndiaxHistory. 0aIndiaxPolitics and governmenty21st century. 0aRoutledge contemporary South Asia series.  aHX 393.5 C34 2015c1hUAAU-Bi0162035229473  aHX 393.5 C34 2015wLCc1i0162035229473d4/11/2016e3/13/2016lON_SHELFmUAAUGn2p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/4/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n89113435bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/2522094